README for Localization Information

Should contain:
- Server requirements for full UTF-8 support
	- If creating database manually, the command to use for MySQL and Postgresql
- Instructions for adding support for new languages:
	- Create a new directory for the locale in the locale/ directory, using the files of the existing locale directories as a template
	- Translate locale.xml and any images or other files in the directory
	- Add your new locale to locale/locales.xml
	- Log in to OJS as the Site Administrator, and select "Languages" to install the new locale 
